laghutthānaḥ śīghram evottiṣṭhet. na tu jṛmbhikāṃ gātramoṭanaṃ kurvann ālasyopahitaś cireṇa. etebhya eva sarvebhyaḥ pūrvam eva.

<commentary>idam aparam abhisaṃkṣipya kathayann āha.

ācāraḥ śikṣaṇīyam. aprameyaḥ asaṃkhyeyaḥ bodhisattvaprātimokśādiṣu pradarśitaḥ. tatsaṃgraharūpaṃ prathamataḥ cittaśodhanam eva ācāram ācaret. niyatam avaśyaṃtayā.</commentary>

sāmānyāpattiśodhanāyāha. triṣkṛtvo rātreḥ, triṣkṛtvo divasasya.